DataElement.preferredDefinition: Not processed or refined.:Any material sample taken from a biological entity for testing, diagnostic, propagation, treatment or research purposes, including a sample obtained from a living organism or taken from the biological object after halting of all its life functions. Biospecimen can contain one or more components including but not limited to cellular molecules, cells, tissues, organs, body fluids, embryos, and body excretory products._A statement or an account describing something._Generic value domain for a java datatype that is a class that represents character strings.
